        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a73" ANNOTATION_REF="a1">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>(You speak) better than the Indians, the Indians would come to you and speak in broken (Arabic), because they learned it only orally</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a74" ANNOTATION_REF="a2">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>They didn't learn the rules and the ways of sentence structuring, but you obviously got properly educated, God bless</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a75" ANNOTATION_REF="a3">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Thank God, really, your Arabic is excellent, God bless</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a76" ANNOTATION_REF="a4">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was living in Ṣabāḥiyya</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a77" ANNOTATION_REF="a5">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, I was young</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a78" ANNOTATION_REF="a6">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Before we didn't # have things like photos or taking photos, so I never had my picture taken up until after I got married</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a79" ANNOTATION_REF="a7">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>These kinds of things were not found, so we did not practice them</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a80" ANNOTATION_REF="a8">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>And our families would not allow us to get photographed ##, only in wedding occasions or if there was travel involved, or something of the sort, only then</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a81" ANNOTATION_REF="a9">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Of course I remember, I was grown when the war happened, I was 15 years old</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a82" ANNOTATION_REF="a10">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>I remember</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a83" ANNOTATION_REF="a70">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>From Iraq?</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a84" ANNOTATION_REF="a11">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, everything (was affected), thank God, I returned to Kuwait, thank God, they were difficult days</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a85" ANNOTATION_REF="a12">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Where? Oh no, I had them after, I got married in '93, after the war</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a86" ANNOTATION_REF="a13">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>No, it was age dependent, I married after (because I was young during the war), thank God</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a87" ANNOTATION_REF="a71">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>#</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a88" ANNOTATION_REF="a72">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>No, thank God, I never experienced this</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a89" ANNOTATION_REF="a14">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Thank God, the most forgiving and merciful, I only felt scared when I son Fahad went to America, as soon as he finished his secondary school he went to America, I was destroyed</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a90" ANNOTATION_REF="a15">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Because why? I had told him, "after you finish university", this was when he was young</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a64" ANNOTATION_REF="a16">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>why b-aʕraf? why the b- for the negation ### also what does she mean</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a91" ANNOTATION_REF="a17">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>And he was my eldest child, now the fear has # here</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a92" ANNOTATION_REF="a18">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>This was a period were I was sufferring, I didn't think about the fact that he was there to study and that he would eventually come back, no, I just wanted him to return</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a93" ANNOTATION_REF="a19">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was scared, honestly, I tell you this was a perios where I was suffering </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a94" ANNOTATION_REF="a20">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>And the telephone and  Whatsapp, he went in 2014</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a95" ANNOTATION_REF="a21">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>The telephone was basically stuck to my head, "Where are you? Where are you? Where are you? Where are you? Where are you?"</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a68" ANNOTATION_REF="a22">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Waw, waw, waw (I was also calling), nothing helped#, I was so tired</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a65" ANNOTATION_REF="a23">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Thank God, he studied the language and got into university for a year, and he had some conditions, and there wasn't any help for him</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a96" ANNOTATION_REF="a24">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>There wasn't anyone to help them there, the matters there were not handled so well</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a97" ANNOTATION_REF="a25">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>He is smart and managed to get into university, and he did he TOEFAL exam, which is the IELTS, he passed successfully </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a98" ANNOTATION_REF="a26">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>But I told him "That's it, come back, come back". This was a period where I was suffering </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a99" ANNOTATION_REF="a27">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>After he came back, he continued (his education), thank God</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a100" ANNOTATION_REF="a28">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>His brother who is younger than him, God bless, he got into # and graduated</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a66" ANNOTATION_REF="a29">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Fahad... God is all knowling, I don't know, but in the end he learned the language, he studied the English language, and he benefitted from it</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a67" ANNOTATION_REF="a30">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Now, he entered university with fortitude (he was amongst the best students), yes he got delayed by two or three years, but then he entered as one of the best students </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a101" ANNOTATION_REF="a31">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>No, thank God, this comes from the person, these are capabilities coming from God</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a102" ANNOTATION_REF="a33">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>God bless, look at you, you were born in '95 and you are working on your doctoral degree, you are still young to be doing this </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a103" ANNOTATION_REF="a34">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>May God help you, and if you complete your doctoral degree ##</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
